n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"583361ea309d7ba952e7ace3b8b39ba16386148a","tid":589001,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:28:43.000Z","msg":"班焦土撚而家開心喇？"},{"pid":"08502bca2723824a74e17e2f5722b5bdb250395b","tid":589001,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"583361ea309d7ba952e7ace3b8b39ba16386148a","tid":589001,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:28:43.000Z","msg":"班焦土撚而家開心喇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:31:33.000Z","msg":"輸係公屋區多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n焦土撚新東已大敗<br />\n本身九西就係十萬左右"},{"pid":"369bff04162f1a0c130d69acbd6b639cff4acd80","tid":589001,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:31:40.000Z","msg":"其實埋飯民堆預左會抄車架啦"},{"pid":"2e830a45473629cdef19f7409da9da6e5fdd801f","tid":589001,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislik